verbose_text: Notably, both CD8 + T cell-sufficient and depleted mice that were vaccinated with GAd-Eecto or GAd-Zvp survived lethal ZIKV challenge (XREF_FIG), indicating a subordinate role for CD8 + T cells in GAd vaccine induced protective immunity.
